OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780611061
OL,3,CPM accuses Musk of trying to 'whip up
OL,4,Cdivision' over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has accused Elon Musk
OL,7,Fof trying to "whip up division" in the
OL,8,FUK over Henry Nowak's murder and said
OL,9,FBritain needs to "assert who we are"
OL,10,Fas "reasonable, tolerant people".
OL,12,FThe billionaire X owner has posted
OL,13,Fnumerous times on his platform about
OL,14,Fthe police response to the stabbing of
OL,15,Fthe teenager in Southampton last year,
OL,16,Fcriticising "how heinously Nowak was
OL,17,Ftreated by the police in his dying
OL,18,Fmoments".
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@_O]qD@ROUqD@dO]rD@DOUrD@`O]xD@
OL,26,AMOUzD@HO]
