PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780611061
OL,3,CPM accuses Musk of trying to 'whip up
OL,4,Cdivision' over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister told reporters
OL,7,Fduring a trip to York on Thursday: "We
OL,8,Fneed to also assert who we are as a
OL,9,Fcountry, because Musk, again, has been
OL,10,Finterfering in our politics in the
OL,11,Flast few days, trying to whip up
OL,12,Fdivision ` that is not who we are in
OL,13,FBritain.
OL,15,F"In Britain, we are reasonable,
OL,16,Ftolerant people.
OL,18,F"When we have a terrible case like
OL,19,FHenry's case, Henry Nowak, we react
OL,20,Fcalmly, as his family have done."
OL,26,@oD@dOUwD@AOUzD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
