PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780611061
OL,3,CPM accuses Musk of trying to 'whip up
OL,4,Cdivision' over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FBut Mr Musk's intervention over Mr
OL,7,FNowak's murder, which also saw him
OL,8,Foffer to fund a private prosecution of
OL,9,FHampshire Constabulary, has prompted
OL,10,Fwhat appears to be Sir Keir's
OL,11,Fstrongest direct condemnation of the
OL,12,Fbillionaire yet.
OL,14,FFinance student Mr Nowak's treatment
OL,15,Fby police has triggered a political
OL,16,Frow, with Sir Keir branding
OL,17,F"unforgiveable" Reform UK leader Nigel
OL,18,FFarage's suggestion that the public
OL,19,Fshould feel "pure, cold rage" about
OL,20,Fthe case.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@OO]{D@MOU{D@]O]
