OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780611061
OL,3,CPM accuses Musk of trying to 'whip up
OL,4,Cdivision' over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FThe Conservatives have called for the
OL,7,Fofficers who arrested Mr Nowak on
OL,8,Ffalse racism claims to face a full
OL,9,Fmisconduct investigation.
OL,11,FAsked about the Tories' demand, Sir
OL,12,FKeir said "there are questions that
OL,13,Fneed to be answered" over the police
OL,14,Fresponse, and added that the
OL,15,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,16,Fshould be given space to "get on with
OL,17,Ftheir job" in investigating the case.
OL,26,@tD@KOUuD@TO]xD@ZOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
