CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780611061
OL,3,CPM accuses Musk of trying to 'whip up
OL,4,Cdivision' over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,F"I think it's right that there may
OL,7,Fneed to be changes and we shouldn't
OL,8,Fshy away from that," the Labour leader
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"But we really need to listen to
OL,12,FHenry's family, because they're asking
OL,13,Fus, as politicians, as leaders, not to
OL,14,Fuse his case to whip up division, not
OL,15,Fto cause disturbances. We have to
OL,16,Flisten to them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@TO]sD@AOU
